Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.54,0:00:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.38,0:00:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people\Nseek the answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.48,0:00:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future --\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.54,0:00:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright,\Nbut I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.54,0:00:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.15,0:00:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.55,0:01:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.99,0:01:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.33,0:01:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.14,0:01:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.44,0:01:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.58,0:01:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really\Nneed everything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.59,0:01:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.76,0:01:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.36,0:01:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.07,0:02:04.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yuba" "Erumalu" "Nanohana" "Katorea"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.57,0:01:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three years have passed since\Na single drop of rain fell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:01:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the kingdom of oases.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:02:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing hope beyond turmoil,\Nthe people took up weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.65,0:02:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The burning land is now\Nenveloped by a sad bellowing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.65,0:02:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a mighty swell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.89,0:02:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, to reach Yuba,\Nwhere the rebel army is,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.09,0:02:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy's group set into the desert...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.66,0:02:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...where numerous, unimaginable\Nhardships fell upon them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Enter the Desert Pirates!\NThe Men Who Live Freely"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.14,0:02:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So hot... Water...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.35,0:02:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Zoro. This heat\Nis too much for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.18,0:02:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act polite. It's stifling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.02,0:02:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! How far did you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.22,0:02:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That side of you is wonderful too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.79,0:02:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.47,0:02:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is much easier\Nthanks to you, Lashes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:03:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But will the others be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.87,0:03:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll just follow the footprints!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.32,0:03:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsunami!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--A tsunami's coming!\N--What's going on, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.19,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it wasn't such\Na good idea after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What wasn't a good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told him not to, but he said he\Nwas so thirsty he couldn't stand it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.13,0:03:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he chomped down on some\Ncactus growing back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.57,0:03:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cactus?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.01,0:03:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.24,0:03:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those round things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.64,0:03:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Those are bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are mezcal cacti! They're\Nused to make hallucination drugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.92,0:03:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.92,0:03:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna drown!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.76,0:03:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Bring it on, if you dare!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.69,0:03:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll beat all of you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.86,0:04:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.20,0:04:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tranquilizer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Do you see Nami's group?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.28,0:04:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn. We're completely\Nseparated from them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And their footprints are disappearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.09,0:04:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I haven't\Nseen Ace for a while, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.13,0:04:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did he disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.43,0:04:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he got separated from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh! What a troublesome big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the ones who got separated!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--All because of you!\N--Quit acting so carefree!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hear something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.79,0:05:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pirate ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aah! It's--!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami and Vivi've been caught!\NOh, and the camel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey! Luffy!\N--Don't be rash!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.33,0:05:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Let's go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.33,0:05:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.11,0:05:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Give-Me-Water!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.38,0:05:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm out of strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.86,0:06:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I just hear something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.31,0:06:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so thirsty I misjudged...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.88,0:06:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, do you have any water?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you didn't come to save us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only came to get water.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.49,0:06:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help, Luffy-san!\NLashes is about to be eaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing's edible?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.68,0:07:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We, the Barbar Sand Pirates, have a saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.58,0:07:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aside from friends, nothing alive\Nin the desert can't be eaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.62,0:07:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll even eat stuff off the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.69,0:07:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll make you sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.43,0:07:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.86,0:07:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a funny pipsqueak!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.73,0:07:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're funny too! Well, let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.27,0:07:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.28,0:07:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Barbarossa, captain of\Nthe Barbar Sand Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, was it? I'm sorry for our\Nrough treatment of your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.42,0:07:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that we're all so hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.66,0:07:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not for you to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.43,0:07:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Captain! We don't have any\Nwood at all to repair our main mast!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.77,0:07:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without a main mast,\Nwe won't have enough thrust!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.50,0:08:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Yeah! What're we gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.37,0:08:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't do something,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're going to die like dogs\Nin the middle of this desert!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We're gonna die like dogs!\N--Huh?! What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.68,0:08:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The Barbar Sand Pirates are gonna die!\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.52,0:08:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We sand pirates are born\Nin sand pirate ships,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we'll die in sand pirate ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Abandoning our ship is unthinkable!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! That's right! We'll die in our ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.30,0:08:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll die like dogs in our ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.87,0:08:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was fate, this was fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.87,0:08:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We sand pirates will never do\Nanything to defy the flow of sand!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't say I didn't warn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is timber at the Meriyasu Oasis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?! I'll rush there real quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the sands've changed lately.\NIt's dangerous for outsiders.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.21,0:09:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm responsible for it! I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.65,0:09:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?! You will?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.15,0:09:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring back wood with this sand-sled.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.39,0:09:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say this is more of\Na canoe than a sled...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.39,0:09:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zaba and Rasa will show you\Nto the Meriyasu Oasis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Rasa?\N--Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.50,0:09:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rasa is our ship's finest sand-sledder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.60,0:09:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sand-sled can carry two people.\NWhat'll you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.94,0:09:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.61,0:09:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, now! Quit saying\Nbaseless things like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll probably be demanding work.\NWant me to go with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.23,0:10:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! That was cool, Rasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The others seem to be outsiders...\Nbut you're from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! How could she tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.28,0:10:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have some\Nexperience with a sand-sled.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll come along.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.88,0:10:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi-chan can't do\Nanything that dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.08,0:10:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! That's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'll come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.39,0:10:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So these go on top of\Nthe sand? How does it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.19,0:10:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pilot the sled.\NI did this once long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.73,0:10:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not too different from a ship.\NThis goes like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.51,0:10:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't waste your strength\Ndoing stupid things!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can rest there, Luffy-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.69,0:11:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's see. I believe\Nthis goes like this and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.83,0:11:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh. Let's go, Zaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.43,0:11:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Rasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.33,0:11:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This feels great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we borrow this,\Ncan't we reach Yuba right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.14,0:11:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to control sand-sleds.\NIt's not something easily mastered.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.55,0:11:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how come you can control it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to practice with a sand-sled\NI received when I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what should we do while we wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.79,0:11:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to eat the camel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Yay! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.23,0:11:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.03,0:11:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't sound like a joke to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.11,0:12:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! What's the big idea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.65,0:12:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Rasa! That's--!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Vivi! We're getting\Npulled in more and more!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quicksand! If we get\Nswallowed into the sand,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.89,0:12:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll never come back out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.23,0:12:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rasa. Wasn't that going too far?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.53,0:12:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If luck's on her side,\Nshe'll make it through alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You know that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.71,0:12:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. As if I'd ever forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.37,0:12:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You alright, Vivi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.87,0:13:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in trouble if we don't do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.94,0:13:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi! Duck!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.81,0:13:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.15,0:13:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite how he seems, you can\Nalways count on Luffy in a pinch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. But what concerns me\Nmore is the desert's fickleness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.73,0:13:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The desert's fickleness?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.66,0:13:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. The desert is honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A slight change in weather or\Npeople's hearts will change it greatly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.81,0:13:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A change in people's hearts?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.74,0:13:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.41,0:14:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! It's them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.81,0:14:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.48,0:14:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Turn to starboard! Hurry!\N--Battle stations!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna get in my way, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.71,0:14:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--There are so many of them!\N--Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.24,0:14:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Desert bandits! Pests who're\Nalways desperately fighting us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conflict seems imminent these days!\NThat has them on edge, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.02,0:15:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you can't move!\NYou're finally ours today!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men! Don't let a single\None of them leave alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our pleasure! Our pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this, a pub?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.84,0:15:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The desert has pit us together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will the desert choose us,\Nthe Barbar Pirates, or you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's let the desert\Ndecide our fate in battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! Fool! The desert'd never choose you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.03,0:15:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.03,0:15:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Grand Dung Beetle!\N--There's a Grand Dung Beetle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.90,0:15:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Grand Dung Beetle?\N--Say what now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.73,0:15:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Desert bugs that haul giant balls of dung!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No less than 100 people a year\Nare squished by their rolling dung!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.08,0:15:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.89,0:16:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! It's headed right for our ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.23,0:16:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, guests...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.43,0:16:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll let you off easy this time!\NYour lives are spared for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That deserves a\Nwarm shower of applause.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.44,0:17:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rasa! Don't you think\Nyou went a little too far?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.88,0:17:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--They're not following!\N--That's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she won't come\Nhowever much we wait,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that's just the level of a person she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We caught up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.08,0:17:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.56,0:17:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This oasis is completely buried in sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.16,0:17:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was once a flourishing city, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.03,0:17:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been here before?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.53,0:17:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people of this city gave me\Na small sand-sled as a memento.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a very long time ago, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.44,0:18:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I stopped by here once with my father
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.08,0:18:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when he was traveling around the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.82,0:18:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, the king told us,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.86,0:18:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"If anything happens to this oasis,\NI will come rushing to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kingdom won't ignore any voice,\Nno matter how small."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.80,0:18:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were that girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.87,0:18:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, this oasis was\Nburied in sand and abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.81,0:18:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every last person in town left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.38,0:18:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I stayed behind\Nand waited for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believed in you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.35,0:18:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the king never came. Nor you, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.33,0:19:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because similar incidents\Nwere happening all over the country
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.83,0:19:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the king was busy every\Nday trying to combat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.60,0:19:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear your excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.17,0:19:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I waited all alone in the\Nmiddle of this vast desert!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, I couldn't\Ndifferentiate between dawn and dusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.65,0:19:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the time Barbarossa took me in,\NI couldn't feel anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.12,0:19:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,not even the midday scorching heat\Nor the freezing cold after sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.86,0:19:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that I was even alive baffled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.97,0:19:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, inside my head,\Nthe king's words continue to ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.34,0:19:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I don't understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.88,0:19:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things were so difficult,\Nso what exactly was I waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.55,0:19:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what kept me going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hate? Anger? Or inexistent hope?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.19,0:20:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.21,0:20:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.71,0:20:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry for making you wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.35,0:20:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.20,0:20:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They sure ran off in a hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.37,0:20:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it's too bad we didn't get\Nto swipe any of their food or water.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.51,0:20:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sand pirates sure have it tough, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.91,0:20:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything living in this\Ndesert has it the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.95,0:21:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, I used to feel this\Ndesert belonged to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I think about it now,\NI feel like that's a bit conceited.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.46,0:21:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, I've come to think that\Nit might not belong to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.37,0:21:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That we're able to live freely\Nbecause it belongs to no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.14,0:21:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think the sea is the same way?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.91,0:21:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.81,0:21:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's something you'll have\Nto find out for yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.32,0:21:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is! We made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.50,0:21:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.18,0:22:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the adventurers\NI dreamed of when I was a child
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.98,0:22:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I continue on to the ends of emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.09,0:22:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I scoop up my hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.09,0:22:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the sand and time\Nthat spills from them
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.70,0:22:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,show me that this is\Nwhat I was born to do
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.71,0:22:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's continue swimming\Nat a near-tumbling speed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.79,0:22:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we wash up someday\Non a white sandy beach
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.56,0:22:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no one knows about
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.25,0:23:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Say, Luffy. Where's your brother?\N--Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.95,0:23:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's worse at directions\Nthan this guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.85,0:23:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Who're you\Ntalking about, Pervy Cook?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.12,0:23:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who else is there besides you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.22,0:23:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I got food and water!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.76,0:23:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Big brother! How?!\N--Got it from the rebel army!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.43,0:23:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.83,0:23:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.36,0:23:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"False Fortitude!\NCamu, Rebel Soldier at Heart!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.97,0:23:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.30,0:23:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
